In a world free from power, relationships would be a cacophony of harmonies.    Powerlessness     w   o   u   l   d     b   e   g   e   t     Driftlessness                          w                        o                        u                        l                        d                          b                        e                        g                        e                        t      Powerlessness    A circle of antipathy and sympathy, weaving webs of wonder.   Power.